Now is not the time to be picky.

530
00:38:04,410 --> 00:38:06,203
- Stop talking nonsense.
- Okay.

531
00:38:06,620 --> 00:38:09,749
A loving couple onscreen together.
It's going to be great.

532
00:38:10,166 --> 00:38:11,584
And great for Hanphil too.

533
00:38:12,585 --> 00:38:13,794
Make sure we're well-prepared.

534
00:38:14,003 --> 00:38:15,171
[chuckles] Okay.

535
00:38:15,337 --> 00:38:16,589
[giggles]

