00:38:27,475 --> 00:38:28,517
[Jeongjae] So?

541
00:38:28,601 --> 00:38:30,186
[Taeho] <i>The host is Professor Kim.</i>

542
00:38:31,103 --> 00:38:32,480
[♪ pensive music plays]

543
00:38:32,563 --> 00:38:33,606
What?

544
00:38:33,731 --> 00:38:36,776
Ms. Cha is aware of it
and still agreed to do it.

545
00:38:38,235 --> 00:38:39,278
[sighs heavily]

546
00:38:39,737 --> 00:38:41,155
They're going to start shooting soon.

547
00:38:41,739 --> 00:38:43,115
Is this really okay?

548
00:38:44,617 --> 00:38:45,826
Thanks for the heads-up.

549
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:48,788
