- [cell phone beeps]

550
00:38:51,165 --> 00:38:52,333
{\an8}[sighs heavily]

551
00:38:55,211 --> 00:38:56,253
[sighs]

552
00:39:00,382 --> 00:39:02,927
[♪ pensive music fades]

553
00:39:03,385 --> 00:39:04,553
Taeho?

554
00:39:06,138 --> 00:39:07,139
Hi.

555
00:39:08,599 --> 00:39:10,142
What were you doing in there?

556
00:39:13,145 --> 00:39:17,024
I was just checking to see
if the rehearsal room needed cleaning.

557
00:39:17,650 --> 00:39:21,612
You know, because it might be messy.

558
00:39:22,863 --> 00:39:23,948
[chuckles softly]

559
00:39:25,407 --> 00:39:26,784
Have you eaten yet?

560
00:39:27,910 --> 00:39:29,328
Lunchtime is almost over.

561
00:39:29,703 --> 00:39:31,247
I haven't eaten yet.

562
00:39:31,997 --> 00:39:33,874
It's late, why haven't you...

563
00:39:34,834 --> 00:39:36,210
Do you want to have lunch

564
00:39:36,460 --> 00:39:37,461
with me?

565
00:39:37,628 --> 00:39:40,714
[♪ intriguing music plays]

566
00:39:41,090 --> 00:39:43,384
- Have you eaten?
- No, I'm starving.

567
00:39:44,927 --> 00:39:45,928
Sounds good.

568
00:39:48,848 --> 00:39:50,057
Let's eat lunch

569
00:39:50,266 --> 00:39:51,308
together.

570
00:39:52,476 --> 00:39:54,270
Okay, let's do that.

571
00:39:55,479 --> 00:39:56,564
[chuckles softly]

572
00:39:57,356 --> 00:40:00,109
[♪ intriguing music continues]

573
00:40:03,863 --> 00:40:04,905
What do you want?

574
00:40:06,073 --> 00:40:07,157
Let's talk.

575
00:40:07,783 --> 00:40:09,493
[♪ intriguing music concludes]

576
00:40:34,518 --> 00:40:36,186
Don't do the KVN documentary.

577
00:40:40,566 --> 00:40:41,609
I have to do it.

578
00:40:41,817 --> 00:40:44,069
- Hanphil needs it.
- [Jeongjae] Don't do it.

579
00:40:44,153 --> 00:40:45,487
It's not worth your time.

580
00:40:46,697 --> 00:40:48,532
- I'll make sure Hanphil...
- No.

581
00:40:48,657 --> 00:40:50,618
I'm going to shoot it, no matter what.

582
00:40:55,247 --> 00:40:57,833
Why would you want to see
that bastard again?

583
00:40:59,877 --> 00:41:01,962
- I don't need to avoid him.
- Come on, Seeum.

584
00:41:02,087 --> 00:41:03,797
[Seeum] If I can generate some interest,

585
00:41:03,923 --> 00:41:05,466
I'll do whatever it takes.

586
00:41:05,633 --> 00:41:07,885
That's how I've always done things.

587
00:41:08,010 --> 00:41:09,386
So don't stand in my way.

588
00:41:09,511 --> 00:41:11,263
Isn't this going overboard?

589
00:41:11,388 --> 00:41:13,724
What about you?
Why are you acting like this?

590
00:41:16,143 --> 00:41:17,353
As if you didn't know.

591
00:41:21,649 --> 00:41:22,858
From now on, just stop.

592
00:41:22,942 --> 00:41:24,109
Just stop?

593
00:41:24,652 --> 00:41:25,694
[Seeum] Yes, stop.

594
00:41:26,028 --> 00:41:28,113
It's my orchestra, I'll handle it.

595
00:41:28,238 --> 00:41:29,949
Stop making me worry, then.

596
00:41:31,200 --> 00:41:34,244
[♪ melancholic music plays]

597
00:41:36,914 --> 00:41:39,667
No matter how hard I try
not to be concerned, I can't help it.

598
00:41:41,502 --> 00:41:43,671
I tell you not to do something,
you don't listen.

599
00:41:43,754 --> 00:41:45,464
I offer help, you reject it.

600
00:41:46,632 --> 00:41:48,258
It's like I'm...

601
00:41:50,344 --> 00:41:52,805
I hate it and it's so frustrating.

602
00:41:54,431 --> 00:41:56,934
But like an idiot,
I can't stop worrying about you.

603
00:42:06,777 --> 00:42:07,903
[sighs heavily]

604
00:42:13,784 --> 00:42:15,119
[sighs]

605
00:42:26,922 --> 00:42:29,508
[♪ melancholic music fades]

606
00:42:37,641 --> 00:42:39,601
Why does Hanphil mean so much to you?

607
00:42:41,270 --> 00:42:43,814
If you leave the orchestra,
then that's the end of it.

608
00:42:49,361 --> 00:42:50,404
[sighs]

609
00:42:53,532 --> 00:42:56,618
You're right.
If I leave, then that's that.

610
00:43:04,793 --> 00:43:05,878
But...

611
00:43:08,172 --> 00:43:10,632
this could be my last orchestra.

612
00:43:12,801 --> 00:43:15,804
[♪ sorrowful piano music plays]

613
00:43:42,790 --> 00:43:45,042
[♪ sorrowful piano music continues]

614
00:44:16,073 --> 00:44:18,408
[♪ sorrowful piano music continues]

615
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:25,791
[Seeum] <i>You're right.</i>

616
00:44:26,458 --> 00:44:27,960
<i>If I leave, then that's that.</i>

617
00:44:28,836 --> 00:44:29,837
<i>But...</i>

618
00:44:33,924 --> 00:44:36,260
<i>this could be my last orchestra.</i>

619
00:44:43,851 --> 00:44:45,769
[♪ sorrowful piano music fades]

620
00:44:45,978 --> 00:44:48,438
- [Yeongmi] <i>Hello.</i>
- [Jiae] <i>Hi, everyone.</i>

621
00:44:48,522 --> 00:44:49,565
[Baha] Hi.

622
00:44:51,525 --> 00:44:54,027
Your makeup looks different today.

623
00:44:54,278 --> 00:44:57,114
We're going to be on TV, so I got it done.

624
00:44:57,197 --> 00:44:59,199
[Jiae] Maybe I should've
gotten mine done too.

625
00:44:59,366 --> 00:45:01,702
We can go tomorrow. They're shooting

626
00:45:02,202 --> 00:45:03,328
up until the concert.

627
00:45:03,412 --> 00:45:05,247
