775
00:53:57,112 --> 00:53:58,530
[sighs heavily]

776
00:54:00,490 --> 00:54:02,367
[bottle spraying]

777
00:54:03,910 --> 00:54:05,453
[sighs heavily]

778
00:54:12,043 --> 00:54:13,169
[knocking on door]

779
00:54:13,545 --> 00:54:14,546
Yes?

780
00:54:15,588 --> 00:54:16,715
It's me.

781
00:54:16,923 --> 00:54:18,007
[door closing]

782
00:54:19,008 --> 00:54:20,009
Get out.

783
00:54:20,301 --> 00:54:21,386
[scoffs heavily]

784
00:54:21,511 --> 00:54:24,305
Do I need the film crew around to see you?

785
00:54:24,431 --> 00:54:26,433
